{"tid":1948290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分析 文宣點做最安全","createTime":"2020-03-29T02:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T21:20:46.000Z","uid":353063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be181c6451eacb2c1741ad86d4abc5b9df7ac991","tid":1948290,"uid":353063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"其實出去街外痴，風險一定大<br />\n最驚啲人係大廈入面痴<br />\n後樓梯一定多家庭主婦睇<br />\n扔完垃圾分分鐘企多陣睇<br />\n反正唔趕時間<br />\n<br />\n另外一個就係每層樓搭lift位<br />\n次次等lift都會睇通告<br />\n一樣道理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外 管理處實會日日清<br />\n去其他樓層要行後樓梯<br />\n好易比CCTV影<br />\n<br />\n放人地屋企門口就唔好啦<br />\n會拎入屋慢慢睇架<br />\n睇到變黃屍就唔好啦<br />\n不過黃屍咁窮<br />\n一定唔會咁做啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n呢啲文宣字體同通告差唔多大就得<br />\n不過要多圖少字<br />\ntarget啲中年人<br />\n同埋最好係解釋性同tvb你看不到的事系列咁<br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"3543c80e0bec0dd291c7d62e2a765102255730c5","tid":1948290,"uid":353063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"P牌自推好似無用<br />\n推"},{"pid":"94a8b73172f3614866fceb0bb8575db6e9518d3f","tid":1948290,"uid":353063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7c80f292299ffeebfa099bb3287c835af11c230","tid":1948290,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用！"},{"pid":"ee3bfcbe0ae2efc0daae879c8e19a4e644403daf","tid":1948290,"uid":209603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf1cea2bc6d460a4631261b3ac379ad7454cc31","tid":1948290,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5f9d6f5f0cba1167589f7c1af3d7437c4b5a3f","tid":1948290,"uid":